### Enhancements

* Add reusable HTTP test server fixtures (`http_test_server` and `session_http_test_server`) to `conda.testing` module for serving mock conda channels and remote files in tests. Fixtures are configurable via `@pytest.mark.http_server_dir()` marker and provide a clean API with `get_url()` helper method. (#15528 via #15529)

