### Docs

* Add comprehensive guide for using HTTP test server fixtures in `docs/source/dev-guide/writing-tests/http-test-server.md`. Includes usage examples, API reference, migration guide from `support_file_server`, and troubleshooting tips. (#15528 via #15529)

